      <acqinfo id="aspace_e96ef0773f2815cf8df8a1e9bfcd1717">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The Yale Library purchased the Pardee papers from Earle and Whitlock's in 1940 and 1944. They were transferred from the Miscellaneous Manuscripts Collection in 1985.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_5686a4ff3bfee31a32458f52f2869750">
